1752
01:12:04,260 --> 01:12:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem mnogi žive.

1753
01:12:05,539 --> 01:12:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što sveta Hildegarda preporuča

1754
01:12:08,500 --> 01:12:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] je umjerenost.

1755
01:12:09,380 --> 01:12:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam kako danas funkcionira

1756
01:12:12,380 --> 01:12:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi u zajednici.

1757
01:12:13,279 --> 01:12:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] Redovito se prežderavamo,

1758
01:12:14,859 --> 01:12:15,939
[SPEAKER_00] ne u naše, u svima.

1759
01:12:15,939 --> 01:12:17,939
[SPEAKER_00] Osim Omnija deo,

1760
01:12:17,939 --> 01:12:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] svaka čast njima.

1761
01:12:18,819 --> 01:12:20,239
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su za modnu reviju.

1762
01:12:20,579 --> 01:12:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno.

1763
01:12:20,960 --> 01:12:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je jedina zajednica

1764
01:12:23,140 --> 01:12:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] i to je jedini nagovori

1765
01:12:25,000 --> 01:12:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje sam uspio naći u postu.

1766
01:12:26,420 --> 01:12:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] I svaka im čast.

1767
01:12:27,279 --> 01:12:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, javno, kredic,

1768
01:12:29,920 --> 01:12:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] Tu Omnija deo.

1769
01:12:31,640 --> 01:12:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] I Frante Vučković,

1770
01:12:32,699 --> 01:12:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] da, on ima ovaj 16-8.

1771
01:12:34,300 --> 01:12:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, mislim koja nije s našeg kanala.

1772
01:12:38,619 --> 01:12:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mi redovito,

1773
01:12:41,159 --> 01:12:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] zbog toga što je gospod tako rekla,

1774
01:12:43,279 --> 01:12:44,520
[SPEAKER_00] postimo o kruhu i vodi,

1775
01:12:44,520 --> 01:12:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad nam je do nečeg jako stalo,

1776
01:12:46,119 --> 01:12:48,479
[SPEAKER_00] uspjevamo se disciplinirati,

1777
01:12:48,479 --> 01:12:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] imati neku jaku ili dijetu,

1778
01:12:50,039 --> 01:12:50,680
[SPEAKER_00] ili post,

1779
01:12:50,680 --> 01:12:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] i onda nastavljamo po starom.

1780
01:12:53,239 --> 01:12:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] To nije zdrava duhovnost.

1781
01:12:55,199 --> 01:12:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zdrava duhovnost je umjerenost.

1782
01:12:57,039 --> 01:12:59,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mislite da je gospod u Međugorje,

1783
01:12:59,359 --> 01:13:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] 81. rekla,

1784
01:13:00,460 --> 01:13:02,100
[SPEAKER_00] postite dva dana o kruhu i vodi,

1785
01:13:02,100 --> 01:13:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] nije.

1786
01:13:02,420 --> 01:13:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] Nego 84. rekla,

1787
01:13:04,760 --> 01:13:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] za jedan dan,

1788
01:13:05,359 --> 01:13:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda kad...

1789
01:13:06,079 --> 01:13:08,439
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, odgali su se u postupnosti.

1790
01:13:08,439 --> 01:13:11,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želite steći krepost umjerenosti,

1791
01:13:11,100 --> 01:13:12,479
[SPEAKER_00] koja je majka svih vrlina,

1792
01:13:12,479 --> 01:13:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] naučite se postupno.

1793
01:13:15,199 --> 01:13:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kroti se.

1794
01:13:15,720 --> 01:13:16,680
[SPEAKER_00] Nekad ti je puno lakše

1795
01:13:16,680 --> 01:13:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] odpostiti o kruhu i vodi

1796
01:13:17,859 --> 01:13:19,180
[SPEAKER_00] i otići u McDonald's poslije,

1797
01:13:19,180 --> 01:13:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] nego ne pojes kolač poslije ručka,

1798
01:13:21,239 --> 01:13:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili za ustavici.

1799
01:13:22,039 --> 01:13:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jel tako?

1800
01:13:23,539 --> 01:13:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] To govori i Sveti Koze Marija je skriva.

1801
01:13:26,119 --> 01:13:27,439
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1802
01:13:27,439 --> 01:13:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] jako je važno

1803
01:13:29,220 --> 01:13:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] da je prehrana

1804
01:13:30,859 --> 01:13:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] povezana

1805
01:13:31,819 --> 01:13:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] i s našom duhovnosti.

1806
01:13:33,640 --> 01:13:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] Sportaši nemao s tim problema,

1807
01:13:35,600 --> 01:13:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] pa od...

1808
01:13:36,220 --> 01:13:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1809
01:13:39,539 --> 01:13:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] jako je važno

1810
01:13:42,699 --> 01:13:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] znati postavice i prema alkoholu.

1811
01:13:45,039 --> 01:13:46,020
[SPEAKER_00] Postoje pitanja,

1812
01:13:46,020 --> 01:13:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] evo, neka koja ste danas javljaju,

1813
01:13:47,579 --> 01:13:47,939
[SPEAKER_00] isto,

1814
01:13:47,939 --> 01:13:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] alkohol i nikotin.

1815
01:13:51,180 --> 01:13:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je zanimljivo.

1816
01:13:52,000 --> 01:13:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da im kokos.

1817
01:13:52,739 --> 01:13:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] Još malo moram i biti gotovo.

1818
01:13:55,220 --> 01:13:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] Nije vam pametno na dugo slavljanje

1819
01:13:58,399 --> 01:13:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam ja,

1820
01:13:58,859 --> 01:14:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] zato sam jednom u pola godine.

1821
01:14:00,619 --> 01:14:04,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mislim da je jako važno

1822
01:14:04,100 --> 01:14:05,680
[SPEAKER_00] da ove stvari usvojimo,

1823
01:14:05,680 --> 01:14:06,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer ovo su stvari

1824
01:14:06,720 --> 01:14:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] koje...

1825
01:14:07,960 --> 01:14:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Alkohol je negdje postao,

1826
01:14:10,119 --> 01:14:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] i tu opet ne govorim

1827
01:14:11,140 --> 01:14:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] o onom javnom vidljivom alkoholizmu.

1828
01:14:13,859 --> 01:14:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] Postoje ljudi koji jako puno piju

1829
01:14:15,899 --> 01:14:18,100
[SPEAKER_00] i uz to rade dobro.

1830
01:14:18,100 --> 01:14:19,680
[SPEAKER_00] To se ne vidi.

1831
01:14:19,680 --> 01:14:21,399
[SPEAKER_00] Stalno su u adrenalinu,

1832
01:14:21,399 --> 01:14:23,899
[SPEAKER_00] ali to jako utiče na tvoj odnos s Bogom.

1833
01:14:23,899 --> 01:14:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] I nije kod svakog isto.

1834
01:14:25,640 --> 01:14:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] Zato Sirak tu daje savjet.

1835
01:14:27,260 --> 01:14:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] Sirak 37, od 27 do 28.

1836
01:14:29,840 --> 01:14:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sine moj,

1837
01:14:30,579 --> 01:14:31,560
[SPEAKER_00] dok si živ,

1838
01:14:31,560 --> 01:14:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] kušaj narav svoju.

1839
01:14:32,800 --> 01:14:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] Vidiš to joj šteti

1840
01:14:34,159 --> 01:14:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] i to joj uskrati.

1841
01:14:35,119 --> 01:14:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije svima sve probitačno,

1842
01:14:37,300 --> 01:14:39,479
[SPEAKER_00] niti je svakom sve po volji.

1843
01:14:39,479 --> 01:14:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš se testirati.

1844
01:14:41,340 --> 01:14:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što ugrožava tvoj odnos s Bogom,

1845
01:14:43,859 --> 01:14:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] nije vrijedno.

1846
01:14:44,760 --> 01:14:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ljudi koji mogu.

1847
01:14:46,319 --> 01:14:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] I sveti Pavo samo o tome govori.

1848
01:14:48,819 --> 01:14:52,479
[SPEAKER_00] Blago tebi ako možeš i savjeste ne optužuje.

1849
01:14:52,479 --> 01:14:55,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pazi da ne bi svog brata

1850
01:14:55,479 --> 01:14:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] ranjene savjesti s tim navuka u grijeh.

1851
01:14:58,220 --> 01:15:00,979
[SPEAKER_00] Mi moramo znati koja je granica.

1852
01:15:00,979 --> 01:15:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ja dolazim,

1853
01:15:04,420 --> 01:15:05,680
[SPEAKER_00] ako popijem, ne znam,

1854
01:15:05,680 --> 01:15:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] neko može stvarno više,

1855
01:15:06,880 --> 01:15:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] neko može manje.

1856
01:15:07,840 --> 01:15:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nekima je to u genima,

1857
01:15:09,340 --> 01:15:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] nekima nije.

1858
01:15:11,880 --> 01:15:13,520
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kaže si Irak,

1859
01:15:13,520 --> 01:15:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] vidi kako tvoja narav reagira na nešto

1860
01:15:17,239 --> 01:15:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] i ako ti to ugrožava odnosu s Bogom.

1861
01:15:19,340 --> 01:15:21,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to ugrožava tvoj odnos,

1862
01:15:21,399 --> 01:15:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] onda to reži.

1863
01:15:22,420 --> 01:15:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] Isto je sa pušenjem.

1864
01:15:25,220 --> 01:15:27,060
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je bilo puno pitanja o tome.

1865
01:15:29,060 --> 01:15:35,359
[SPEAKER_00] Pušenje po službeni nauk crkve je da pušenje samo po sebi nije grijeh,

1866
01:15:35,359 --> 01:15:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] nego prekomjerno pušenje je ovisnost.

1867
01:15:38,260 --> 01:15:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] Problem je što nikotin stvarno izaziva vrlo jaku ovisnost.

1868
01:15:42,699 --> 01:15:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je ovisnost, je grijeh.

1869
01:15:46,319 --> 01:15:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je svetaca koji su pušili, imali su granicu.

1870
01:15:49,680 --> 01:15:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] Padre pio je šmrkao duhan,

1871
01:15:53,460 --> 01:15:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad je imao posebno teške bolove.

1872
01:15:55,960 --> 01:15:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, istinu ja govorim.

1873
01:15:57,500 --> 01:15:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj Pierre Georges Frassati,

1874
01:15:59,699 --> 01:16:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] o kojem se piše knjiga, uvijek je sa lulicom.

1875
01:16:01,619 --> 01:16:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Pavao VI.

1876
01:16:03,699 --> 01:16:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] Papa Montini je pušio.

1877
01:16:05,500 --> 01:16:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Tako imao teške odluke.

1878
01:16:07,659 --> 01:16:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] Neki jednom je jedan kardinal bio kraj njega.

1879
01:16:11,079 --> 01:16:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao mu je, sveti oče,

1880
01:16:12,720 --> 01:16:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] pa ne priliči, kako to vi pušite, to je porok.

1881
01:16:15,279 --> 01:16:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] A Pavao VI. mu je rekao,

1882
01:16:17,460 --> 01:16:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa da je to porok, ti bi ga sigurno imao.

1883
01:16:19,460 --> 01:16:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, oču vam reći.

1884
01:16:24,960 --> 01:16:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nešto postaje ovisnost, reži skroz.

1885
01:16:29,180 --> 01:16:31,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ja uvijek savjetujem pušačima,

1886
01:16:31,319 --> 01:16:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] i sam sam bio pušač dugo,

1887
01:16:32,880 --> 01:16:34,220
[SPEAKER_00] pušio sam cigarete,

1888
01:16:34,220 --> 01:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam se zavjetao do braka.

1889
01:16:36,000 --> 01:16:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ako već nekad ti paše taj gušt,

1890
01:16:38,720 --> 01:16:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] početi pušiti kubanke, one velike ili lulu.

1891
01:16:41,260 --> 01:16:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] Skupo je, nećeš puno pušiti.

1892
01:16:43,739 --> 01:16:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno će ti biti užitak,

1893
01:16:45,239 --> 01:16:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] znači nisi rob,

1894
01:16:46,140 --> 01:16:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] moraš odvojiti vrijeme za to,

1895
01:16:47,739 --> 01:16:49,180
[SPEAKER_00] moraš to pripremiti.

1896
01:16:49,180 --> 01:16:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jer danas se u cigarete stavlja svašta.

1897
01:16:51,920 --> 01:16:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] I vi mi kažete,

1898
01:16:52,640 --> 01:16:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] baba u Ljubuškom u Posušiju ima 90 godina,

1899
01:16:55,880 --> 01:16:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne gasi cigaru,

1900
01:16:57,159 --> 01:16:58,479
[SPEAKER_00] to nije isti duhan više.

1901
01:16:58,479 --> 01:16:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] I ne stavlja se ista stvar.

1902
01:16:59,840 --> 01:17:01,399
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, dobro procijenite.

1903
01:17:01,399 --> 01:17:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] Najbolje je ne pušiti.

1904
01:17:03,180 --> 01:17:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ako već pušite,

1905
01:17:05,159 --> 01:17:09,600
[SPEAKER_00] nađite da to bude opet da ste vi gospodari toga.

1906
01:17:09,600 --> 01:17:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ripeger ima jedan baš dobar nagovor o tome.

1907
01:17:14,420 --> 01:17:16,479
[SPEAKER_00] Tu su i Petar i David,

1908
01:17:16,479 --> 01:17:17,600
[SPEAKER_00] pa možda da prevedete.

1909
01:17:17,600 --> 01:17:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] Baš je rašlanio šta je grijeh

1910
01:17:19,279 --> 01:17:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] i dokle je grijeh i zašto.

1911
01:17:20,840 --> 01:17:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] Po nauku crkvi.

1912
01:17:21,779 --> 01:17:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] Da, evo,

1913
01:17:22,699 --> 01:17:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] osam minuta trajete,

1914
01:17:24,699 --> 01:17:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] šta je to vama.

1915
01:17:25,420 --> 01:17:27,100
[SPEAKER_00] Pa objavite,

1916
01:17:27,100 --> 01:17:28,180
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je to nešto

1917
01:17:28,180 --> 01:17:29,479
[SPEAKER_00] oko čeg se dosta rasprava

1918
01:17:29,479 --> 01:17:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] i vode u zajednici.

1919
01:17:30,399 --> 01:17:31,060
[SPEAKER_00] Najbolje ne.

1920
01:17:31,060 --> 01:17:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] Sve šta te udalje od Boga

1921
01:17:32,619 --> 01:17:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] prekriži.

1922
01:17:34,500 --> 01:17:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] I peto,

1923
01:17:36,300 --> 01:17:37,600
[SPEAKER_00] odnošno zadnje,

1924
01:17:37,600 --> 01:17:40,600
[SPEAKER_00] otuđenje od stvorenoga,

1925
01:17:40,600 --> 01:17:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] od prirode,

1926
01:17:41,319 --> 01:17:42,100
[SPEAKER_00] od stvorenja.

1927
01:17:42,100 --> 01:17:46,279
[SPEAKER_00] Knjiga,

1928
01:17:46,279 --> 01:17:47,180
[SPEAKER_00] moje obsjednuće.

1929
01:17:47,180 --> 01:17:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam slušao

1930
01:17:48,619 --> 01:17:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] Francesca Vajasusa

1931
01:17:49,699 --> 01:17:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bio obsjednuta

1932
01:17:50,539 --> 01:17:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] 70 legija demona

1933
01:17:52,039 --> 01:17:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] uživo na kaptolu

1934
01:17:54,159 --> 01:17:54,720
[SPEAKER_00] kad je imao

1935
01:17:54,720 --> 01:17:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] predstavljanje knjige.

1936
01:17:56,439 --> 01:17:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što je zanimljivo,

1937
01:17:57,479 --> 01:17:58,140
[SPEAKER_00] rekao je,

1938
01:17:58,140 --> 01:17:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] da uvijek imao

1939
01:17:59,300 --> 01:18:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] demonološke reakcije

1940
01:18:00,500 --> 01:18:01,439
[SPEAKER_00] na svetu vodu,

1941
01:18:01,439 --> 01:18:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] na svece,

1942
01:18:02,340 --> 01:18:03,100
[SPEAKER_00] na Mariju,

1943
01:18:03,100 --> 01:18:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] na krunicu,

1944
01:18:03,739 --> 01:18:04,439
[SPEAKER_00] na egzorcista

1945
01:18:04,439 --> 01:18:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi molio,

1946
01:18:05,140 --> 01:18:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali da bi imao

1947
01:18:06,420 --> 01:18:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] jake demonološke reakcije

1948
01:18:08,539 --> 01:18:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] i kada bi se našao

1949
01:18:09,819 --> 01:18:10,979
[SPEAKER_00] u prekrasnoj prirodi.

1950
01:18:10,979 --> 01:18:11,979
[SPEAKER_00] Zato,

1951
01:18:11,979 --> 01:18:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer priroda

1952
01:18:13,000 --> 01:18:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] govori o Bogu.

1953
01:18:14,739 --> 01:18:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo danas

1954
01:18:17,319 --> 01:18:19,060
[SPEAKER_00] izgubili kontakt s prirodom.

1955
01:18:19,060 --> 01:18:20,380
