01:23:24,699 --> 01:23:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] isposlovan u Carigradu,

2176
01:23:25,920 --> 01:23:27,020
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam koji način.

2177
01:23:27,020 --> 01:23:28,939
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim se otvara sirotište,

2178
01:23:28,939 --> 01:23:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] odgalište mladih,

2179
01:23:30,220 --> 01:23:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] bolnica,

2180
01:23:31,159 --> 01:23:32,479
[SPEAKER_00] pučka kuhinja,

2181
01:23:32,479 --> 01:23:34,060
[SPEAKER_00] stanovi za radnike.

2182
01:23:34,060 --> 01:23:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo zvono,

2183
01:23:35,899 --> 01:23:36,859
[SPEAKER_00] koje je zazvonilo

2184
01:23:36,859 --> 01:23:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] u Turskoj Bosni tad.

2185
01:23:38,359 --> 01:23:39,060
[SPEAKER_00] Škola,

2186
01:23:39,060 --> 01:23:40,939
[SPEAKER_00] zanadske radionice,

2187
01:23:40,939 --> 01:23:41,779
[SPEAKER_00] pivovara.

2188
01:23:41,779 --> 01:23:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] Htio ih je skinuti sa šljivovice,

2189
01:23:43,500 --> 01:23:44,560
[SPEAKER_00] svi su bili mrtvi pijani,

2190
01:23:44,560 --> 01:23:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] pa ih je prebacio na pivu.

2191
01:23:46,140 --> 01:23:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ozbiljno.

2192
01:23:46,819 --> 01:23:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Taj tekst je fenomenal,

2193
01:23:48,800 --> 01:23:49,979
[SPEAKER_00] ali nemamo vremena sad.

2194
01:23:49,979 --> 01:23:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] Oni je rekao,

2195
01:23:53,199 --> 01:23:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] počnite sušiti šljive,

2196
01:23:54,380 --> 01:23:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] da ih spasi od tog,

2197
01:23:55,500 --> 01:23:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] da ne rade šljivovicu.

2198
01:23:57,920 --> 01:23:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] I oni dolaze za njemu,

2199
01:23:58,859 --> 01:23:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] on presrtan,

2200
01:23:59,579 --> 01:24:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] istrijebio sam tu ovisnost,

2201
01:24:00,960 --> 01:24:02,060
[SPEAKER_00] i oni dolaze za njemu,

2202
01:24:02,060 --> 01:24:03,560
[SPEAKER_00] dođe mu neki pijan

2203
01:24:03,560 --> 01:24:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže vam,

2204
01:24:04,699 --> 01:24:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] brate,

2205
01:24:05,220 --> 01:24:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] vranjo,

2206
01:24:05,819 --> 01:24:06,899
[SPEAKER_00] bog te blagoslovio,

2207
01:24:06,899 --> 01:24:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] mi bi uvijek ispekli

2208
01:24:08,260 --> 01:24:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] svu šljivu

2209
01:24:08,779 --> 01:24:09,979
[SPEAKER_00] i popili je do Božića,

2210
01:24:09,979 --> 01:24:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] a sad kad imamo suhu,

2211
01:24:11,159 --> 01:24:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] možemo peć cijele godine.

2212
01:24:12,619 --> 01:24:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se on bičevao,

2213
01:24:15,180 --> 01:24:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno cijelu noć

2214
01:24:16,380 --> 01:24:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] za pokoru,

2215
01:24:17,180 --> 01:24:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] ali ih je uspio preodgojiti,

2216
01:24:18,899 --> 01:24:20,939
[SPEAKER_00] tako da ih je prebacio na pivu.

2217
01:24:22,199 --> 01:24:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bila vrhunska pija.

2218
01:24:23,359 --> 01:24:24,060
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite ovo,

2219
01:24:24,060 --> 01:24:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] kovačnice,

2220
01:24:25,100 --> 01:24:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] pilane,

2221
01:24:25,699 --> 01:24:27,439
[SPEAKER_00] pčelinjaci,

2222
01:24:27,439 --> 01:24:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] rasadnici.

2223
01:24:28,359 --> 01:24:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] Za njegova života

2224
01:24:30,239 --> 01:24:31,560
[SPEAKER_00] je Marija zvijezda

2225
01:24:31,560 --> 01:24:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] imala preko 200 redovnika

2226
01:24:33,840 --> 01:24:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] i postala najveći samostan

2227
01:24:35,539 --> 01:24:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] na svijetu.

2228
01:24:36,260 --> 01:24:37,939
[SPEAKER_00] Iz ničega,

2229
01:24:37,939 --> 01:24:38,939
[SPEAKER_00] iz drvene kolibe.

2230
01:24:38,939 --> 01:24:41,520
[SPEAKER_00] 27.3.1899.

2231
01:24:41,520 --> 01:24:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] Prva električna žarulja

2232
01:24:43,199 --> 01:24:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] u Bosni i Hercegovini.

2233
01:24:44,340 --> 01:24:46,060
[SPEAKER_00] Već 1910.

2234
01:24:46,060 --> 01:24:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] 300 konskih snaga hidroelektrana

2235
01:24:48,279 --> 01:24:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] osvijetila cijelu Banja Luku,

2236
01:24:49,859 --> 01:24:50,899
[SPEAKER_00] prije Zagreba,

2237
01:24:50,899 --> 01:24:51,859
[SPEAKER_00] cijela Banja Luka,

2238
01:24:52,199 --> 01:24:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] je imala struju.

2239
01:24:53,659 --> 01:24:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] 1904. prvi most u Banja Luci,

2240
01:24:56,159 --> 01:24:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] most Svetog Bernarda.

2241
01:24:57,319 --> 01:25:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] 1907. prva visokoškolska institucija,

2242
01:25:02,380 --> 01:25:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] filozofsko-teološki fakultet.

2243
01:25:04,640 --> 01:25:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, tu je sad još cijeli dalje niz,

2244
01:25:08,779 --> 01:25:09,279
[SPEAKER_00] da ne idem.

2245
01:25:09,279 --> 01:25:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek je došao na ništa,

2246
01:25:11,359 --> 01:25:12,479
[SPEAKER_00] a znate šta je ništa?

2247
01:25:12,479 --> 01:25:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] To nije ovo naše ništa.

2248
01:25:14,659 --> 01:25:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo baš ništa.

2249
01:25:16,279 --> 01:25:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Štadler, drugi velikan duha,

2250
01:25:21,500 --> 01:25:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] isto prelazi

2251
01:25:23,039 --> 01:25:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] Savu,

2252
01:25:24,739 --> 01:25:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi u Bosnu,

2253
01:25:25,760 --> 01:25:26,399
[SPEAKER_00] u Sarajevo,

2254
01:25:26,399 --> 01:25:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] kao nadbisu na 800 katolika.

2255
01:25:28,619 --> 01:25:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta znači 800 katolika u tom gradu?

2256
01:25:31,619 --> 01:25:35,060
[SPEAKER_00] I čovjek je mogao gledati kako je sve ovo.

2257
01:25:35,060 --> 01:25:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mogao je mrmljati ljudska perspektiva.

2258
01:25:37,239 --> 01:25:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] Popis stanovništa 1910. manje od 30 godina.

2259
01:25:42,859 --> 01:25:44,899
[SPEAKER_00] On je došao 1882.

2260
01:25:44,899 --> 01:25:49,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako, 18460 muslimana,

2261
01:25:50,859 --> 01:25:52,399
[SPEAKER_00] 8460 pravoslavnih,

2262
01:25:52,399 --> 01:25:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] 17922 rimo katolika.

2263
01:25:56,399 --> 01:25:57,899
[SPEAKER_00] Izgradio je katedralu,

2264
01:25:57,899 --> 01:25:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] bogosloviu,

2265
01:25:59,279 --> 01:26:00,520
[SPEAKER_00] sjemenište u Travniku,

2266
01:26:00,520 --> 01:26:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] dva velika sirotišta,

2267
01:26:01,819 --> 01:26:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] čardak Doloruzu,

2268
01:26:03,180 --> 01:26:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] dom časnih sestara,

2269
01:26:04,239 --> 01:26:05,979
[SPEAKER_00] osnovao red časnih sestara.

2270
01:26:05,979 --> 01:26:10,060
[SPEAKER_00] Hranio je na tisuće djece svih vjeroispovijesti.

2271
01:26:10,060 --> 01:26:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što je gradio,

2272
01:26:11,680 --> 01:26:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] gradio je bez novaca.

2273
01:26:15,180 --> 01:26:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] Danas kažu nema novaca.

2274
01:26:16,579 --> 01:26:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je li nema novaca,

2275
01:26:18,260 --> 01:26:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] ja idem.

2276
01:26:19,140 --> 01:26:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] A djetet ima tri para tenisica

2277
01:26:22,260 --> 01:26:24,359
[SPEAKER_00] i mijenja mobitel svake dvije godine.

2278
01:26:24,359 --> 01:26:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi moji, jel ste vi svjesni?

2279
01:26:26,579 --> 01:26:31,439
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže mi jedna članica naša zajednica,

2280
01:26:31,439 --> 01:26:34,100
[SPEAKER_00] čija je unuka u jednom austrijskom gradu,

2281
01:26:34,100 --> 01:26:36,819
[SPEAKER_00] da su morali sad za Halloween

2282
01:26:36,819 --> 01:26:38,939
[SPEAKER_00] piti crvenu tekućinu,

2283
01:26:38,939 --> 01:26:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja je predstavljala krv

2284
01:26:40,119 --> 01:26:42,399
[SPEAKER_00] i raditi zabave obred zazivanja duhova.

2285
01:26:42,399 --> 01:26:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Morali.

2286
01:26:44,020 --> 01:26:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] I normalno, dva dana ne može spavat, djete.

2287
01:26:46,340 --> 01:26:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi kažemo, teško je, ne može se.

2288
01:26:51,460 --> 01:26:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nego je to ona bježanija

2289
01:26:54,300 --> 01:26:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] o kojoj smo pričali.

2290
01:26:55,260 --> 01:26:58,640
[SPEAKER_00] Bez novaca.

2291
01:26:58,640 --> 01:27:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] Imam tu pismo koje je pisao

2292
01:27:00,579 --> 01:27:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] biskupu Jure u Štrosmeru,

2293
01:27:02,000 --> 01:27:03,020
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio pun novaca.

2294
01:27:03,020 --> 01:27:04,979
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je toliko domišljato.

2295
01:27:04,979 --> 01:27:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, jutro dok sam bio u molitvi,

2296
01:27:07,039 --> 01:27:08,020
[SPEAKER_00] sjetih se vas.

2297
01:27:08,020 --> 01:27:10,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kak će ovaj sad odbiti.

2298
01:27:10,140 --> 01:27:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] I onda još u pismo on kaže,

2299
01:27:12,859 --> 01:27:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] treba i ova njiva, treba i krani djecu,

2300
01:27:14,880 --> 01:27:15,979
[SPEAKER_00] treba kupiti krave.

2301
01:27:15,979 --> 01:27:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] I samo imao jednu molitvu koju je molio svaki dan.

2302
01:27:19,279 --> 01:27:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine, molim te da umrem bez dugova.

2303
01:27:21,760 --> 01:27:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog mu je dao da je šest meseci prije smrti

2304
01:27:24,619 --> 01:27:26,020
[SPEAKER_00] uspio vratiti sve dugove.

2305
01:27:26,020 --> 01:27:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] Sve šta je izgradio, je izgradio bez novaca,

2306
01:27:28,720 --> 01:27:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] a kad sam snimao intervju sa kardinalom Vinkom Puljićem,

2307
01:27:31,960 --> 01:27:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] onda mi je on rekao,

2308
01:27:33,800 --> 01:27:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] mi ne stignemo pokreći šta je on sve izgradio.

2309
01:27:40,100 --> 01:27:42,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Imao je Božju perspektivu.

2310
01:27:42,819 --> 01:27:47,399
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo postati ljudi koji gledaju Božim očima.

2311
01:27:50,479 --> 01:27:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je rekao jednu jako tužnu rečenicu

2312
01:27:52,960 --> 01:27:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] s kojom ću završiti ovo predavanje.

2313
01:27:54,680 --> 01:27:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] Hoće li gospodin naći vjere na zemlji?

2314
01:27:58,199 --> 01:28:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo da je vjera jedino bogatstvo koje je potrebno.

2315
01:28:02,180 --> 01:28:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini resurs koji su imali Franz Faner i Josip Stadler

2316
01:28:06,039 --> 01:28:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] je bila vjera.

2317
01:28:09,399 --> 01:28:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] Isus da danas dođe bi našao puno novaca,

2318
01:28:13,039 --> 01:28:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] možda je puno zajednica,

2319
01:28:14,659 --> 01:28:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] možda je puno obraćenih,

2320
01:28:16,739 --> 01:28:21,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali pitanje je hoće li gospodin naći vjere na zemlji.

2321
01:28:21,180 --> 01:28:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

